      • Response

        public Response(Response.ResponseType responseType,
                java.util.Set<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,com.google.gson.JsonElement>> model,
                java.lang.String err,
                boolean[] preFeedback,
                boolean[] postFeedback)
        Constructor of a successful Response.
        Parameters:
        responseType - The response type given by the Haskell API. If the methods are found to be equivalent, this should be Equiv. Otherwise it should be NotEquiv.
        model - The counterexample found by the Haskell API, or null if the methods were found to be equivalent.
        err - Error from the checker.
        preFeedback - Feedback booleans about the precondition.
        postFeedback - Feedback booleans about the postcondition.
